WEBVTT

01:42.979 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.130 --> 01:48.990
[Episode 18]

01:49.110 --> 01:52.080
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

01:56.229 --> 01:56.729
Does it hurt?

01:59.270 --> 01:59.710
No.

02:04.190 --> 02:04.790
Wen.

02:07.470 --> 02:08.070
I'm sorry.

02:08.830 --> 02:09.460
I scared you.

02:17.400 --> 02:18.570
When I was six,

02:19.550 --> 02:20.680
my mom left my dad.

02:23.190 --> 02:25.510
My dad's... very stubborn.

02:26.190 --> 02:27.320
He is

02:27.950 --> 02:28.980
very extreme.

02:29.910 --> 02:30.579
Since

02:31.350 --> 02:32.520
I was a kid, my mom and I

02:32.520 --> 02:33.190
lived in misery.

02:35.829 --> 02:36.770
If my mom added

02:37.110 --> 02:38.230
too much salt in the food,

02:38.840 --> 02:40.300
or if I woke up one minute late,

02:40.829 --> 02:41.430
or even

02:42.030 --> 02:43.310
if I just put the cup

02:43.350 --> 02:44.340
on the table too hard,

02:44.370 --> 02:45.260
he would...

02:46.450 --> 02:47.950
insult me harshly

02:49.190 --> 02:49.990
and slap me.

02:56.110 --> 02:57.270
When that man said

02:58.120 --> 02:58.950
he could abuse

02:59.170 --> 03:00.590
his child as he wished,

03:01.310 --> 03:02.470
it really triggered me.

03:05.210 --> 03:06.040
Because that was

03:06.070 --> 03:07.190
how I spent my childhood.

03:30.150 --> 03:30.910
What are you doing?

03:33.380 --> 03:34.660
Where did you get the money?

03:35.310 --> 03:36.070
Where did you steal it from?

03:37.290 --> 03:38.030
I'm asking you!

03:38.390 --> 03:39.030
Where did you steal it from?

03:41.540 --> 03:42.390
I didn't steal it.

03:43.210 --> 03:44.270
Then how did you get it?

03:45.670 --> 03:46.310
I saved it.

03:47.750 --> 03:48.460
You saved it?

03:50.170 --> 03:51.560
Why did you save so much money?

03:52.880 --> 03:53.560
Tell me.

03:54.150 --> 03:54.740
Come here.

03:54.860 --> 03:55.720
Who said you can go?

03:56.390 --> 03:57.270
Are you going to buy tickets

03:57.310 --> 03:58.340
to look for your mom?

03:59.630 --> 04:00.400
Come here.

04:03.430 --> 04:04.490
You're just like your mom!

04:05.580 --> 04:06.460
Ungrateful.

04:17.070 --> 04:18.040
So later,

04:19.540 --> 04:20.290
my mom left.

04:21.839 --> 04:22.580
I didn't blame her.

04:23.810 --> 04:24.600
But

04:25.530 --> 04:27.110
my dad was even harsher to me.

04:30.750 --> 04:31.480
He said

04:31.970 --> 04:32.790
I was the way I am

04:32.830 --> 04:33.830
because my mom spoiled me.

04:34.490 --> 04:35.290
Now that

04:36.150 --> 04:37.340
no one's protecting me,

04:38.630 --> 04:39.990
of course he became worse.

04:45.150 --> 04:46.230
What happened after?

04:47.150 --> 04:48.070
Have you

04:48.950 --> 04:50.230
seen your mom after that?

04:52.590 --> 04:53.150
Yes.

04:55.810 --> 04:57.350
One time, I couldn't take it anymore.

04:58.030 --> 04:59.120
I took all my pocket money

04:59.150 --> 04:59.870
to find her.

05:02.470 --> 05:03.470
But near her home,

05:04.310 --> 05:05.140
I saw her

05:05.430 --> 05:06.320
bringing

05:06.350 --> 05:07.980
a boy about my age home.

05:16.550 --> 05:17.250
Just in time.

05:17.310 --> 05:18.510
Granny can persuade my dad.

05:21.630 --> 05:23.260
Are you that eager to go to the police academy?

05:25.710 --> 05:26.910
That boy

05:28.050 --> 05:29.610
is the child of her current husband.

05:32.030 --> 05:34.350
They were carrying the same bag,

05:35.310 --> 05:36.230
talking and laughing.

05:42.100 --> 05:42.680
When they

05:42.710 --> 05:43.850
were about to go upstairs,

05:43.990 --> 05:44.990
my mom suddenly turned around

05:46.110 --> 05:46.950
and saw me.

05:48.260 --> 05:49.909
I was so happy, I...

05:50.950 --> 05:52.000
I wanted to rush up

05:52.030 --> 05:52.940
to let her hug me.

05:53.909 --> 05:54.530
But...

05:56.960 --> 05:58.030
she didn't recognize me.

06:19.840 --> 06:20.870
Her eyes...

06:22.600 --> 06:23.720
just slipped past me,

06:26.230 --> 06:27.330
not even stopping for a second.

06:30.910 --> 06:31.750
Wen.

06:36.940 --> 06:38.430
I'm fine. I...

06:40.909 --> 06:41.470
I'm fine.

06:42.710 --> 06:43.270
It was

06:43.310 --> 06:44.210
a long time ago.

06:44.870 --> 06:46.120
It's been a while since I thought about it.

06:47.620 --> 06:48.580
If...

06:49.590 --> 06:51.110
you need any help,

06:52.420 --> 06:53.659
you can look for me.

06:57.500 --> 06:57.990
Okay.

07:00.670 --> 07:01.500
Wen.

07:01.710 --> 07:02.670
The police needs you for mediation

07:02.670 --> 07:03.640
in the meeting room.

07:03.750 --> 07:04.370
Yan.

07:04.570 --> 07:05.830
You're a witness, so you must go too.

07:05.830 --> 07:06.750
I'll go with you.

07:06.960 --> 07:07.390
Let's go.

07:11.830 --> 07:13.220
It's all clear now.

07:14.010 --> 07:14.760
First,

07:14.790 --> 07:16.060
you hurt your child.

07:16.440 --> 07:17.330
You were angry

07:17.650 --> 07:19.050
and hit him first.

07:19.760 --> 07:20.930
Then you also hurt him.

07:21.860 --> 07:23.020
He beat me

07:23.040 --> 07:24.030
senseless.

07:24.050 --> 07:25.020
I don't know.

07:25.050 --> 07:26.740
I just took something by me.

07:27.430 --> 07:28.610
Besides, officer,

07:29.030 --> 07:30.250
this is also a kind

07:30.560 --> 07:31.810
of self-defense, no?

07:32.550 --> 07:33.480
According to

07:33.500 --> 07:34.260
the child protection law,

07:34.710 --> 07:35.760
when the legal rights

07:35.790 --> 07:36.830
of a minor is violated,

07:37.270 --> 07:38.830
any organization or individual

07:39.030 --> 07:41.030
has the right to intervene

07:41.710 --> 07:42.880
or file a report

07:42.909 --> 07:44.300
to the relevant agencies.

07:46.870 --> 07:47.890
Mr. Wen's behavior

07:47.909 --> 07:49.060
was indeed overboard.

07:49.800 --> 07:50.790
But Mr. Lin,

07:51.590 --> 07:52.720
you're also responsible.

07:52.930 --> 07:53.750
Responsible?

07:54.220 --> 07:54.990
For what?

07:55.030 --> 07:55.710
I spent a fortune

07:55.730 --> 07:56.370
for his operation,

07:56.400 --> 07:57.450
but he wouldn't listen!

07:57.700 --> 07:59.260
Also, who doesn't beat their kids?

07:59.350 --> 08:00.240
What's wrong with me beating

08:00.270 --> 08:00.720
my own kid?

08:00.760 --> 08:01.350
Enough!

08:01.950 --> 08:03.200
Domestic violence is illegal.

08:03.890 --> 08:04.630
Let me tell you.

08:04.670 --> 08:05.910
Behave or there's no more negotiation.

08:07.640 --> 08:09.260
I'll pay for the child's operation.

08:09.910 --> 08:11.660
I'll take care of the post-op medication

08:11.690 --> 08:12.860
and treatment too.

08:16.130 --> 08:16.950
Also,

08:17.900 --> 08:18.830
I'm warning you.

08:19.310 --> 08:21.050
If you hit your son again,

08:21.830 --> 08:23.510
I will make you pay.

08:25.230 --> 08:26.160
What do you mean?

08:26.850 --> 08:27.940
Is that a threat?

08:28.390 --> 08:29.230
You don't deserve

08:29.910 --> 08:30.780
to be a father.

08:32.770 --> 08:33.390
Mr. Wen.

08:34.190 --> 08:34.830
Look.

08:35.030 --> 08:36.679
The kid is waiting for the operation.

08:37.789 --> 08:39.049
Why don't we talk it out

08:39.419 --> 08:40.130
and settle?

08:56.350 --> 08:57.190
Is something on your mind?

08:59.200 --> 08:59.870
No.

09:00.720 --> 09:02.580
Something happened in the hospital today.

09:03.720 --> 09:05.340
Wen Peng got into a fight

09:06.410 --> 09:07.870
with a patient's family.

09:09.530 --> 09:10.170
Why?

09:10.720 --> 09:12.350
The patient is a little boy.

09:12.810 --> 09:14.280
And

09:14.710 --> 09:16.450
the boy's dad beat him.

09:16.880 --> 09:17.790
When I was

09:17.830 --> 09:19.260
trying to stop him,

09:19.390 --> 09:20.850
Wen Peng rushed over

09:20.910 --> 09:21.720
and they started fighting.

09:21.750 --> 09:22.950
Wen even got injured.

09:23.670 --> 09:25.280
He isn't usually so rash.

09:25.800 --> 09:27.070
I only found out later

09:27.090 --> 09:28.260
that it's because

09:29.050 --> 09:31.110
his dad beat him up as a kid,

09:31.200 --> 09:32.820
and his mom didn't protect him.

09:32.950 --> 09:33.960
He may be traumatized

09:34.000 --> 09:34.790
in this aspect.

09:34.810 --> 09:36.080
When he saw that,

09:36.180 --> 09:37.900
he was reminded of his childhood.

09:38.330 --> 09:40.030
He was always beaten up as a kid?

09:43.390 --> 09:44.550
Poor thing.

09:45.560 --> 09:47.080
I didn't expect his background

09:47.110 --> 09:47.910
to be like this.

09:50.350 --> 09:51.250
Does your heart ache?

09:53.550 --> 09:54.830
What heartache?

09:55.140 --> 09:56.530
I'm just sympathizing with him.

09:59.080 --> 10:00.000
What about you?

10:00.590 --> 10:01.920
Have you found Ding Jing?

10:03.220 --> 10:03.990
Not yet.

10:04.470 --> 10:05.170
It's okay.

10:06.700 --> 10:07.720
Take your time.

10:07.750 --> 10:09.230
You will find her.

10:11.350 --> 10:13.020
If I can't catch her,

10:13.180 --> 10:14.950
I can't let it go.

10:16.630 --> 10:18.690
Anyway, I’m quite relieved now.

10:19.130 --> 10:20.500
With Captain Jiang's protection,

10:20.530 --> 10:21.560
I'm the safest person

10:21.590 --> 10:22.680
in the world.

10:23.100 --> 10:24.040
You're glib.

10:29.880 --> 10:31.390
It's safe. I'll protect you.

10:32.330 --> 10:33.330
Never be scared.

10:43.370 --> 10:44.150
Bye.

10:45.780 --> 10:46.440
I'll see you off.

10:49.150 --> 10:50.190
Just two steps?

10:53.520 --> 10:54.620
I'm here.

10:57.390 --> 10:58.880
Go inside and warm yourself up.

11:00.820 --> 11:01.790
My place is too cold.

11:01.820 --> 11:02.890
There's no heater.

11:03.160 --> 11:04.570
What place did you rent?

11:04.620 --> 11:06.030
How's there no heater?

11:06.030 --> 11:06.550
Yeah.

11:06.580 --> 11:07.460
It's shabby and cold.

11:07.560 --> 11:08.340
It's miserable.

11:09.020 --> 11:09.910
I'll go take a look.

11:11.020 --> 11:12.910
What... What's there to see?

11:12.940 --> 11:13.830
I'll see how

11:13.850 --> 11:14.930
shabby and cold it is.

11:28.210 --> 11:29.560
You...

11:49.570 --> 11:51.200
How can you live like that?

11:52.040 --> 11:53.980
I just sleep here.

11:56.340 --> 11:58.660
Is there a water heater?

11:59.290 --> 12:00.680
It isn't installed yet.

12:01.230 --> 12:02.570
Then how do you shower?

12:04.030 --> 12:06.120
I just... use cold water.

12:06.640 --> 12:07.550
Showering

12:07.590 --> 12:08.790
with cold water in winter?

12:08.910 --> 12:10.000
What about your leg?

12:10.030 --> 12:11.190
Aren't you injured?

12:13.160 --> 12:14.100
How did you know?

12:17.670 --> 12:18.990
You've been spying on me,

12:19.010 --> 12:19.650
huh?

12:23.800 --> 12:24.600
No.

12:25.060 --> 12:25.900
I...

12:27.990 --> 12:29.220
I'm a doctor.

12:29.250 --> 12:30.420
I can tell...

12:31.050 --> 12:31.820
just by looking.

12:33.850 --> 12:35.410
You can see it through my pants?

12:37.480 --> 12:38.550
So you've been looking.

12:39.250 --> 12:40.390
Go, go, go.

12:40.570 --> 12:41.580
Already? Want to sit for a while?

12:41.630 --> 12:42.230
Sit?

12:42.260 --> 12:43.020
Sit where?

12:43.490 --> 12:44.450
I'll take you to buy stuff.

12:44.480 --> 12:44.920
Let's go.

12:45.450 --> 12:46.450
Take me to buy stuff?

12:52.720 --> 12:54.030
9.9 yuan for two.

12:58.750 --> 12:59.910
What's the use of this bowl?

12:59.930 --> 13:01.010
This bowl's for...

13:01.040 --> 13:01.970
for soup.

13:02.590 --> 13:03.400
These are

13:03.470 --> 13:05.130
forks and spoons.

13:07.250 --> 13:08.470
Buy this gray one.

13:09.920 --> 13:10.520
This one.

13:11.320 --> 13:12.440
I'll buy you a set.

13:15.990 --> 13:17.340
Do I need so many?

13:17.830 --> 13:18.790
It's a set.

13:18.820 --> 13:21.210
How can you eat instant noodles every day?

13:22.000 --> 13:22.980
I'll buy one more set.

13:24.070 --> 13:25.770
Will you entertain the guests?

13:26.310 --> 13:27.190
Yes, you.

13:28.590 --> 13:30.100
I'm not going to your house.

13:38.430 --> 13:39.200
I think

13:39.230 --> 13:40.460
this is enough.

13:40.720 --> 13:41.760
The tableware's enough.

13:43.030 --> 13:43.870
Jiang Chengyi.

13:44.290 --> 13:45.680
Have you ever sat on

13:46.200 --> 13:47.250
a beanbag?

13:47.270 --> 13:48.290
It's really comfy.

13:48.310 --> 13:48.910
Don't

13:48.950 --> 13:50.550
doctors say not to sit on these

13:50.570 --> 13:52.400
because it's bad for your spine?

13:52.510 --> 13:53.760
It's okay sometimes.

13:53.790 --> 13:54.390
Try it.

13:58.350 --> 13:59.250
Right?

13:59.950 --> 14:00.880
Then I'll buy one.

14:02.820 --> 14:03.230
This...

14:03.300 --> 14:04.160
How much is it?

14:05.430 --> 14:06.770
[Price: 1,888 yuan]

14:06.870 --> 14:08.000
1,888 yuan?

14:08.030 --> 14:09.300
It's too expensive.

14:10.110 --> 14:10.960
After I buy it,

14:11.110 --> 14:12.610
I'll add a label for you:

14:12.640 --> 14:14.170
"Only for Dr. Lu."

14:15.000 --> 14:15.840
And

14:16.150 --> 14:17.920
you can come use it whenever.

14:19.800 --> 14:21.580
Then I'll...

14:21.600 --> 14:22.710
invest in it.

14:23.160 --> 14:24.520
Write down the product code later.

14:27.260 --> 14:27.820
Let's go.

14:28.050 --> 14:28.720
Let's go.

14:30.490 --> 14:31.720
It's hard to get up.

14:33.470 --> 14:34.320
Give me a hand.

14:41.540 --> 14:42.610
Why are you here?

14:43.040 --> 14:43.840
What do you think?

14:43.870 --> 14:45.110
Are you getting up?

14:45.750 --> 14:46.970
People are watching.

14:46.990 --> 14:48.220
Get up now.

14:49.080 --> 14:50.100
Give me another hand.

14:54.450 --> 14:55.150
What?

14:55.170 --> 14:55.790
Let's go.

15:02.010 --> 15:02.670
Today,

15:02.710 --> 15:03.990
I want to tell you

15:04.070 --> 15:05.580
about one of the most

15:05.750 --> 15:06.600
famous

15:06.750 --> 15:08.390
and controversial experiments

15:08.430 --> 15:09.120
in psychology,

15:10.880 --> 15:12.170
the Stanford prison experiment.

15:13.350 --> 15:15.230
The design experiment in this prison

15:15.250 --> 15:16.390
is quite simple.

15:17.030 --> 15:18.230
A basement was designed

15:18.250 --> 15:19.200
into a prison.

15:19.350 --> 15:19.990
They recruited

15:20.020 --> 15:21.390
24 male college students,

15:21.830 --> 15:23.030
who were randomly assigned

15:23.350 --> 15:26.040
to the role of prisoner or prison guard.

15:26.730 --> 15:28.650
Prison guards patrolled eight hours a day,

15:28.910 --> 15:30.230
while prisoners were imprisoned

15:30.250 --> 15:31.480
for 24 hours.

