-Yu Bofeng's the most handsome!
-Yu Bofeng's the most handsome!

15:42.150 --> 15:43.990
-Yu Bofeng's the most handsome!
-Yu Bofeng's the most handsome!

15:44.310 --> 15:45.550
Everything was normal

15:45.630 --> 15:47.570
on the first day of the experiment.

15:47.710 --> 15:49.530
From the next day,

15:49.670 --> 15:52.590
the guards started to assault the prisoners,

15:52.490 --> 15:56.080
[Stanford Prison Experiment]

15:53.350 --> 15:55.070
and the prisoners started to show

15:55.090 --> 15:56.270
abnormal emotional reactions.

15:56.790 --> 15:58.410
In the next few days,

15:58.490 --> 15:59.770
the assaults got

15:59.830 --> 16:01.230
more violent and cruel.

16:01.350 --> 16:03.010
What happened to the prisoners?

16:02.430 --> 16:05.330
[Stanford Prison Experiment]

16:03.070 --> 16:04.870
Their sense of self

16:04.910 --> 16:06.950
started to wane with time.

16:07.210 --> 16:08.120
Yu Bofeng!

16:08.190 --> 16:08.950
So the whole experiment

16:09.000 --> 16:10.100
headed towards chaos.

16:14.430 --> 16:15.510
Yu Bofeng!

16:15.570 --> 16:16.390
Yu Bofeng?

16:19.750 --> 16:20.590
Yu Bofeng!

16:20.610 --> 16:21.510
I'll give you five minutes

16:21.530 --> 16:22.730
to deal with the situation outside.

16:23.420 --> 16:24.890
Don't come back if you can't.

