16:41.070 --> 16:42.100
Sorry, Professor Yu.

16:42.310 --> 16:44.440
In the future,

16:44.470 --> 16:45.860
I'll ask my management team

16:46.020 --> 16:47.510
to guard the door.

16:47.680 --> 16:48.630
Then no one can affect

16:48.630 --> 16:49.230
the classes.

16:49.560 --> 16:50.550
Management team?

16:51.140 --> 16:51.720
Isn't it

16:51.750 --> 16:52.710
chaotic enough with you alone?

16:53.520 --> 16:54.440
Let me tell you.

16:54.740 --> 16:55.400
This is the first

16:55.440 --> 16:56.390
and the last time.

16:56.880 --> 16:58.090
If you can't settle it,

16:58.120 --> 16:59.210
don't come to class anymore.

17:00.110 --> 17:00.430
Okay.

17:00.480 --> 17:01.150
I got it, Professor Yu.

17:01.640 --> 17:02.210
I promise.

17:04.089 --> 17:05.220
Today, I talked about

17:05.349 --> 17:06.640
the Stanford prison experiment.

17:06.670 --> 17:07.780
Were you listening?

17:08.069 --> 17:08.599
Of course.

17:08.630 --> 17:10.150
I was focused throughout.

17:10.540 --> 17:11.730
Then tell me

17:11.950 --> 17:13.560
why kind college students

17:13.589 --> 17:15.420
became assaulters?

17:17.430 --> 17:18.510
That's because...

17:18.560 --> 17:19.510
the amount of power

17:19.670 --> 17:20.710
and environment

17:21.109 --> 17:22.270
have a strong influence

17:22.300 --> 17:23.589
on a person's behavior.

17:23.930 --> 17:24.900
Don't recite the text.

17:25.630 --> 17:27.369
Tell me how you feel.

17:27.910 --> 17:28.760
This way,

17:28.790 --> 17:30.330
it'll help you sculpt

17:30.360 --> 17:31.490
your character.

17:35.090 --> 17:37.490
Is it because those people

17:38.170 --> 17:39.360
stayed in the basement

17:39.390 --> 17:40.150
without the sun for long,

17:40.190 --> 17:41.160
so they were...

17:41.970 --> 17:43.100
in a bad mood?

17:44.340 --> 17:45.060
Right?

17:47.270 --> 17:47.850
Yes.

17:49.950 --> 17:51.130
Really?

17:52.750 --> 17:54.390
So sunbathing's useful?

17:59.460 --> 18:00.790
Professor Yu, I got it.

18:00.830 --> 18:02.500
Maybe it's not just because

18:02.630 --> 18:03.430
of sunlight.

18:04.350 --> 18:06.030
Maybe it's because of the space.

18:06.370 --> 18:08.100
It's too narrow.

18:08.700 --> 18:09.760
So the people inside

18:09.790 --> 18:10.400
were

18:10.450 --> 18:11.730
driven crazy.

18:12.900 --> 18:14.460
It could also be the food.

18:15.310 --> 18:15.920
What you eat—

18:15.950 --> 18:16.750
Yu Bofeng.

18:18.920 --> 18:19.710
I don't mean

18:19.710 --> 18:21.010
to hurt you.

18:21.070 --> 18:22.140
I think

18:22.310 --> 18:25.100
hard work is important.

18:25.270 --> 18:27.010
But the direction of your efforts

18:27.310 --> 18:28.070
is more important.

18:29.500 --> 18:30.270
To be honest,

18:30.270 --> 18:31.510
I think you're suitable to be

18:31.510 --> 18:32.790
an actor with a strong fanbase.

18:33.470 --> 18:35.020
While you still have fans,

18:35.150 --> 18:36.110
make more money.

18:36.130 --> 18:37.520
Then find a good woman,

18:37.630 --> 18:38.880
get married, and have kids.

18:39.030 --> 18:39.980
Live a cozy life.

18:40.230 --> 18:40.830
Isn't that great?

18:41.110 --> 18:41.580
Right?

18:42.750 --> 18:43.550
But Ms. Yu,

18:44.030 --> 18:44.870
what you said

18:44.910 --> 18:46.230
isn't the life I want.

18:49.200 --> 18:51.040
I'm not a performance teacher,

18:51.840 --> 18:53.000
but

18:53.010 --> 18:54.110
I can responsibly

18:54.150 --> 18:55.010
tell you...

18:57.550 --> 18:59.200
that you can't act as

18:59.880 --> 19:00.680
a serial killer.

19:04.560 --> 19:05.350
Ms. Yu.

19:06.460 --> 19:07.970
I know I'm not gifted.

19:09.270 --> 19:10.870
I'm far from mastering that role.

19:11.170 --> 19:12.440
But I believe

19:12.470 --> 19:13.510
I can get what I want

19:13.530 --> 19:15.050
through my efforts.

19:15.880 --> 19:17.500
I won't give up no matter what.

19:17.550 --> 19:19.530
It's not about giving up or not.

19:19.670 --> 19:21.190
It's about a person's IQ,

19:21.270 --> 19:22.160
mind,

19:22.190 --> 19:23.430
logical thinking, understanding—

19:32.410 --> 19:34.270
But I admire this attitude

19:34.270 --> 19:35.030
of yours.

19:35.150 --> 19:36.440
How about this, Yu Bofeng?

19:36.670 --> 19:37.300
You've taken

19:37.300 --> 19:37.950
quite a few

19:37.950 --> 19:39.070
classes so far.

19:39.190 --> 19:40.870
Go back and digest the content

19:40.950 --> 19:41.870
and prepare for

19:41.910 --> 19:42.930
your audition.

19:43.630 --> 19:45.550
You should stop

19:45.950 --> 19:46.950
taking my classes.

19:49.420 --> 19:51.460
Good luck for your audition.

20:07.660 --> 20:08.610
Thank you.

20:10.830 --> 20:11.540
Thank you, Ms. Yu.

20:35.680 --> 20:36.940
I've checked Yu Bofeng.

20:36.960 --> 20:38.140
I don't think he's questionable.

20:38.590 --> 20:39.220
Okay.

20:40.880 --> 20:41.440
Jiang.

20:41.520 --> 20:42.190
I found something.

20:43.360 --> 20:43.910
What's wrong?

20:43.990 --> 20:45.150
Hao and I

20:45.150 --> 20:46.950
checked the surveillance footage

20:46.950 --> 20:48.670
an hour before Ding Jing disappeared.

20:48.750 --> 20:49.350
We found someone.

20:49.470 --> 20:50.180
Take a look.

20:58.230 --> 20:58.880
This?

20:59.360 --> 21:00.110
At the beginning,

21:00.110 --> 21:01.430
we invested all our energy

21:01.470 --> 21:03.190
on the suspect, Ding Jing.

21:03.430 --> 21:04.550
But Hao and I rewatched this

21:04.590 --> 21:05.900
over the past two days.

21:05.990 --> 21:06.900
We realized this person

21:06.930 --> 21:09.160
has been following Lu Yan and Ding Jing.

21:09.580 --> 21:10.580
The surveillance shows that

21:10.630 --> 21:12.750
since Lu Yan entered the subway station,

21:12.770 --> 21:14.610
they've been watching at the back.

21:14.780 --> 21:17.270
After Ding Jing pushed Lu Yan into the subway track,

21:17.340 --> 21:18.530
she fled quickly,

21:18.750 --> 21:20.530
and this person went after Ding Jing

21:20.630 --> 21:21.610
out of the station.

21:23.760 --> 21:25.500
They're great at covering their tracks.

21:26.510 --> 21:27.190
First...

21:27.190 --> 21:28.030
through

21:28.050 --> 21:29.030
another entrance,

21:29.080 --> 21:30.020
they entered the alley

21:30.020 --> 21:31.100
Ding Jing entered.

21:33.490 --> 21:36.040
Then, they waited two hours after Ding Jing left

21:36.130 --> 21:37.040
before they left.

21:38.910 --> 21:40.870
We compared the surveillance footage.

21:42.640 --> 21:44.460
I think this person's back

21:44.630 --> 21:46.610
is quite similar to the murderer

21:47.070 --> 21:47.630
of Wang Qianqian.

21:55.790 --> 21:57.060
More importantly,

21:57.510 --> 21:59.070
I found that this person's physique

21:57.580 --> 22:00.330
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

21:59.070 --> 22:01.020
is very similar to the one

22:01.220 --> 22:02.580
who pretended to be Deng Man.

22:03.500 --> 22:04.370
Indeed.

22:05.270 --> 22:07.650
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

22:05.470 --> 22:06.100
Great timing.

22:06.120 --> 22:07.600
Check her movements

22:07.680 --> 22:08.700
to see if she went

22:08.790 --> 22:09.790
to Jifu Village.

22:09.810 --> 22:10.500
Okay.

22:29.160 --> 22:30.780
Can you say something?

22:32.790 --> 22:33.640
Why did you

22:33.670 --> 22:34.510
kidnap me here?

22:35.360 --> 22:36.580
Do you want money

22:36.610 --> 22:37.300
or...

22:37.460 --> 22:38.360
Just tell me

22:38.390 --> 22:39.930
what you want.

22:40.020 --> 22:41.910
Who asked you to kidnap me?

22:43.090 --> 22:44.660
Can you say something?

23:09.420 --> 23:12.050
Can you say something!

24:06.100 --> 24:07.860
Are you working for him?

24:09.220 --> 24:10.910
You want money, right?

24:12.550 --> 24:13.880
I have money. I have money.

24:13.920 --> 24:15.240
I'll give it to you.

24:16.800 --> 24:18.280
How much did he pay you?

24:18.300 --> 24:19.400
I'll pay you double.

24:21.360 --> 24:22.610
Triple! Four times!

24:23.220 --> 24:25.410
I-I'll give you however much you want!

24:26.410 --> 24:27.520
Let's make a deal.

24:27.810 --> 24:28.880
Let me out.

24:28.910 --> 24:30.290
Call my dad.

24:30.680 --> 24:32.030
As long as you let me out,

24:32.460 --> 24:34.140
he'll pay you however much you want.

24:35.000 --> 24:35.880
Okay?

24:59.390 --> 25:00.210
Fine.

25:01.450 --> 25:02.350
Tell him

25:02.910 --> 25:04.680
I have the evidence.

25:05.400 --> 25:07.230
He gave me the video of Deng Man

25:07.320 --> 25:08.830
being forced to death.

25:09.030 --> 25:10.160
He was also involved.

25:15.810 --> 25:17.230
You want me dead, huh?

25:19.560 --> 25:20.160
Fine.

25:21.570 --> 25:23.480
I'll take him with me even if I die.

25:23.640 --> 25:25.680
I'll take him with me even if I go to hell.

25:36.840 --> 25:37.720
What are you doing?

25:38.880 --> 25:39.650
What are you doing?

26:00.740 --> 26:03.830
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

26:05.700 --> 26:06.780
Xiaoman, can you skate?

26:06.800 --> 26:07.560
No.

26:08.570 --> 26:09.460
I heard there's

26:09.490 --> 26:10.770
a new skating rink here.

26:10.990 --> 26:12.440
After you recover,

26:12.470 --> 26:13.150
I'll take you there.

26:13.400 --> 26:14.230
Sure.

26:14.950 --> 26:16.810
Mr. Wen, can you skate?

26:17.490 --> 26:18.780
I...

26:19.930 --> 26:20.860
I can't skate well.

26:21.040 --> 26:22.580
Is skating safe?

26:22.750 --> 26:23.270
Yes,

26:23.390 --> 26:24.190
very safe.

26:24.610 --> 26:26.890
I'll help you put on your protective gear.

26:27.260 --> 26:28.610
It won't hurt even if you fall.

26:28.790 --> 26:29.190
Okay.

26:29.470 --> 26:30.560
Hello, Ms. Lu.

26:31.710 --> 26:32.560
How are you today?

26:32.590 --> 26:33.310
Feeling better?

26:33.550 --> 26:34.180
Yes.

26:34.350 --> 26:35.390
Mr. Wen said

26:35.420 --> 26:36.520
when I recover,

26:36.550 --> 26:37.790
he'll take me skating.

26:39.190 --> 26:40.550
Then get well soon

26:40.580 --> 26:41.640
and let him take you skating,

26:41.670 --> 26:42.310
okay?

26:42.390 --> 26:43.060
Okay.

26:48.850 --> 26:50.400
I come to see him

26:50.950 --> 26:52.100
after I'm done with work.

26:52.340 --> 26:53.460
Xiaoman's mom can also

26:53.490 --> 26:54.270
get some rest.

26:57.260 --> 26:58.130
By the way,

26:58.510 --> 26:59.520
I heard his operation

26:59.550 --> 27:00.320
was postponed to the day after tomorrow.

27:01.140 --> 27:01.850
Yes.

27:02.020 --> 27:03.850
After what happened yesterday,

27:04.180 --> 27:05.680
all his pre-operation prep

27:05.790 --> 27:06.390
and tests

27:06.430 --> 27:07.470
have to be redone.

27:08.410 --> 27:09.790
I'm going on a business trip then.

27:10.150 --> 27:10.470
I'm worried...

27:10.510 --> 27:10.990
Wen.

27:11.340 --> 27:11.950
Don't worry.

27:12.270 --> 27:12.950
I'm here.

27:12.970 --> 27:14.280
I heard from Xiaoman's mom that

27:14.310 --> 27:15.630
you paid for all the fees

27:15.670 --> 27:17.110
for his post-op treatment

27:17.110 --> 27:18.960
and follow-up checkups.

27:19.330 --> 27:21.060
You've done a lot for him.

27:22.820 --> 27:24.720
Compared to the pain he suffered,

27:24.760 --> 27:26.040
this is nothing.

27:28.710 --> 27:29.540
Actually,

27:30.070 --> 27:31.390
you've helped him a lot too.

27:32.230 --> 27:32.960
Logically,

27:33.110 --> 27:33.960
you didn't have to

27:33.990 --> 27:35.000
interfere yesterday.

27:35.020 --> 27:36.110
What are you talking about?

27:36.490 --> 27:37.570
As long as he's my patient,

27:37.600 --> 27:38.590
it's my business.

27:39.270 --> 27:40.240
But really,

27:40.310 --> 27:41.190
I need to thank you

27:41.230 --> 27:42.070
on behalf of Xiaoman.

27:43.150 --> 27:43.880
It's no problem.

27:45.260 --> 27:46.630
I'm actually helping myself too.

27:50.630 --> 27:51.780
Are you free tonight?

27:51.820 --> 27:52.970
Let's eat together.

27:54.930 --> 27:55.600
Okay.

27:56.960 --> 27:57.770
Lu Yan.

27:59.820 --> 28:00.530
Are you busy?

28:01.190 --> 28:02.150
Why are you here?

28:02.170 --> 28:03.050
Well...

28:03.540 --> 28:04.140
Yes.

28:04.140 --> 28:06.060
I need to talk to you about something.

28:06.590 --> 28:07.510
What is it?

28:08.220 --> 28:08.890
Are you free?

28:09.540 --> 28:10.170
I...

28:11.070 --> 28:11.500
Yes.

28:14.030 --> 28:14.950
Go ahead.

28:15.200 --> 28:16.930
I can spend more time with Xiaoman.

28:17.390 --> 28:17.990
Let's meet another day.

28:25.440 --> 28:26.350
He cares a lot

28:26.350 --> 28:27.110
about that kid.

28:28.420 --> 28:29.060
Let's go.

28:31.280 --> 28:33.250
I've checked some surveillance footage these days.

28:33.450 --> 28:35.120
There's someone weird.

28:37.920 --> 28:38.810
Have you seen them?

28:42.150 --> 28:42.740
No.

28:44.490 --> 28:46.270
Where was this?

28:47.200 --> 28:48.470
This is the day Ding Jing pushed you

28:48.550 --> 28:49.190
at the subway station.

28:49.310 --> 28:49.830
They were there too.

28:50.800 --> 28:51.660
I don't remember.

28:51.750 --> 28:52.900
It's too blurry.

28:53.430 --> 28:53.880
It's okay.

28:53.910 --> 28:54.830
Stay alert.

28:54.850 --> 28:55.780
Tell me if you meet

28:55.950 --> 28:56.560
this person.

28:58.710 --> 29:00.210
Did you drive today?

29:00.350 --> 29:00.830
Yes.

29:01.030 --> 29:01.570
What's wrong?

29:01.600 --> 29:03.190
If you aren't busy,

29:03.210 --> 29:05.060
can you take me somewhere?

29:05.090 --> 29:06.090
I want to buy something.

29:06.120 --> 29:06.770
Sure.

29:07.120 --> 29:07.480
Let's go.

29:14.400 --> 29:15.280
It's here.

29:16.720 --> 29:17.680
Which one?

29:18.630 --> 29:19.960
I don't know how to choose.

29:19.990 --> 29:20.870
You know this, right?

29:21.530 --> 29:22.600
It's not about hardness.

29:21.620 --> 29:25.820
[Decoration]

29:22.670 --> 29:23.110
It's not a melon.

29:23.110 --> 29:23.680
Is it?

29:23.710 --> 29:24.700
Yeah, you can pump it.

29:26.960 --> 29:28.160
This one...

29:30.070 --> 29:31.310
Do you think this looks good

29:31.310 --> 29:32.030
or

29:32.390 --> 29:33.030
this one?

29:33.990 --> 29:34.550
This one.

29:34.570 --> 29:35.110
This one?

29:35.350 --> 29:36.250
Okay, I'll listen to you.

29:36.950 --> 29:37.960
Xiaoman said,

29:37.990 --> 29:38.880
once he's discharged,

29:38.910 --> 29:40.450
he wanted to learn basketball the most.

29:40.990 --> 29:42.430
That kid likes basketball?

29:42.720 --> 29:43.550
He thinks

29:43.590 --> 29:44.840
the tallest and strongest in their class

29:44.870 --> 29:46.160
all play basketball.

29:46.310 --> 29:47.830
So he wants to be like them.

29:48.550 --> 29:49.590
He wants to protect his mom.

29:51.470 --> 29:52.710
Children's wishes

29:52.750 --> 29:54.580
are simple and pure.

29:54.740 --> 29:56.940
It's to protect someone important to you.

29:57.610 --> 29:58.820
That's just like you.

29:59.390 --> 29:59.670
Yeah.

29:59.670 --> 30:01.280
I've always been pure.

30:01.540 --> 30:02.510
I just want to protect

30:02.510 --> 30:03.270
people I cherish.

30:05.310 --> 30:05.970
Do you know that?

30:10.020 --> 30:10.620
Yes.

30:10.770 --> 30:15.880
[Decoration] [Bath]

30:11.950 --> 30:12.960
Let's go pay.

30:13.110 --> 30:13.650
Let's go.

30:15.940 --> 30:18.280
[Children's Section]

30:28.420 --> 30:30.500
Thanks for sending me back, Captain Jiang.

30:31.510 --> 30:32.830
Thanks for inviting me to dinner.

30:35.720 --> 30:36.810
I'll head in.

30:37.800 --> 30:38.490
Wait.

30:39.730 --> 30:41.490
This kid also has a gift.

30:43.910 --> 30:44.390
Look.

30:47.110 --> 30:47.610
You...

30:47.640 --> 30:49.090
When did you buy it?

30:49.130 --> 30:50.180
Doesn't it look like you?

30:52.030 --> 30:53.620
It's dressed like me.

30:53.690 --> 30:54.310
Yeah.

30:54.440 --> 30:55.680
I bought the doctor one.

30:56.850 --> 30:58.270
So cute.

30:59.730 --> 31:00.750
Didn't you say

31:01.060 --> 31:01.980
you didn't have

31:02.160 --> 31:03.460
soft toys as a kid?

31:03.740 --> 31:04.990
I should buy it for you now that you're grown up.

31:09.330 --> 31:11.080
Yeah, I haven't bought one in a long time.

31:12.790 --> 31:13.440
Do you like it?

31:15.790 --> 31:16.790
I love it.

31:19.630 --> 31:20.620
Jiang Chengyi.

31:23.020 --> 31:23.720
Thank you.

31:25.910 --> 31:27.490
Go in. See you tomorrow.

31:28.280 --> 31:29.270
See you tomorrow.

31:32.810 --> 31:33.540
Bye.

31:33.570 --> 31:34.210
Bye.

31:39.870 --> 31:40.450
Good night.

31:41.150 --> 31:41.790
Good night.

32:17.530 --> 32:18.570
Good morning.

32:49.560 --> 32:50.470
Jiang Chengyi.

32:53.250 --> 32:55.610
Jiang Chengyi!

33:00.850 --> 33:01.540
What's up?

33:02.280 --> 33:03.270
Time to get up.

33:06.940 --> 33:07.520
Morning.

33:08.230 --> 33:08.850
Morning.

33:09.820 --> 33:10.790
Is it that cold?

33:11.210 --> 33:12.660
It's so cold in my room.

33:15.440 --> 33:18.460
You gave me a gift yesterday.

33:18.590 --> 33:19.730
I'll treat you to a meal today.

33:20.340 --> 33:20.940
Sure.

33:21.680 --> 33:22.390
What are we eating?

33:22.790 --> 33:23.740
Come to my place.

33:23.770 --> 33:24.720
It's all done.

33:24.930 --> 33:25.770
Eat at your place?

33:26.440 --> 33:27.380
Okay, I'm coming.

33:27.430 --> 33:28.070
Come on.

33:31.610 --> 33:32.720
Think about it.

33:32.990 --> 33:33.640
Have these two

33:33.640 --> 33:34.630
come to your shop?

33:36.830 --> 33:37.440
Well...

33:38.110 --> 33:39.030
What am I looking at?

33:39.700 --> 33:40.660
It's so dark.

33:40.800 --> 33:41.520
Tell me.

33:41.850 --> 33:42.760
Where are their faces?

33:44.400 --> 33:45.160
Sir.

33:45.390 --> 33:46.650
How long have you been running this shop?

33:47.470 --> 33:48.170
I...

33:48.200 --> 33:49.470
opened it when I was young.

33:49.580 --> 33:50.780
Who usually comes here?

33:50.950 --> 33:52.360
It's usually just people

33:52.390 --> 33:53.870
from our village.

33:54.350 --> 33:54.990
Sir.

33:55.130 --> 33:56.590
Have you seen any unfamiliar faces

33:56.610 --> 33:57.440
in the past two days?

33:57.460 --> 33:58.760
People not from the village.

34:00.210 --> 34:01.340
No, no...

34:01.360 --> 34:02.830
That's really rare.

34:04.610 --> 34:05.170
Sir.

34:05.290 --> 34:06.160
These photos

34:06.190 --> 34:07.010
aren't clear.

34:07.030 --> 34:08.520
I'll describe her for you.

34:09.230 --> 34:10.080
A young lady

34:10.110 --> 34:10.800
about...

34:10.909 --> 34:11.600
this tall,

34:11.949 --> 34:12.940
with an average build.

34:12.960 --> 34:14.590
Please try to recall it.

34:15.070 --> 34:15.760
A girl?

34:15.790 --> 34:16.070
Yes.

34:16.070 --> 34:16.840
Wearing a cap

34:16.909 --> 34:17.560
and a mask.

34:18.070 --> 34:18.780
A girl.

34:19.510 --> 34:20.710
She's wearing a cap and a mask

34:20.750 --> 34:22.389
so others can't see her face.

34:23.030 --> 34:23.760
Think about it.

34:26.389 --> 34:27.230
I remember.

34:27.270 --> 34:28.040
Yeah?

34:31.449 --> 34:32.429
Last night,

34:33.000 --> 34:34.500
I was about to close.

34:34.630 --> 34:35.929
A girl came in.

34:35.949 --> 34:37.340
So I'd to serve her.

34:37.389 --> 34:39.219
Miss, what do you want to buy?

34:39.239 --> 34:40.830
She didn't say a word.

34:41.270 --> 34:42.739
She took a few bottles of water

34:42.830 --> 34:44.060
and some bread

34:44.110 --> 34:45.780
and left after leaving 100 yuan.

34:45.920 --> 34:46.679
She left?

34:46.909 --> 34:48.060
Do you know where she went?

34:48.270 --> 34:49.080
No.

34:49.110 --> 34:50.810
I went after her.

34:50.909 --> 34:52.449
Miss, your money!

34:52.469 --> 34:53.960
Your change!

34:54.150 --> 34:54.800
She didn't look back.

34:54.830 --> 34:55.870
She ran so fast

34:55.889 --> 34:56.719
towards north.

34:56.739 --> 34:57.400
To the north?

34:58.030 --> 34:58.580
Sir.

34:58.630 --> 35:00.310
Is there any village in the north?

35:00.430 --> 35:01.910
Village? No.

35:02.310 --> 35:03.880
A long time ago,

35:03.950 --> 35:06.000
there was an industrial park.

35:06.020 --> 35:07.230
It's deserted now.

35:07.600 --> 35:10.090
It's quite far from here.

35:12.220 --> 35:12.810
Okay.

35:12.950 --> 35:13.480
Thank you.

35:13.550 --> 35:14.280
No problem.

35:14.310 --> 35:15.170
Keep these photos.

35:15.270 --> 35:16.390
Our contact info's on it.

35:16.470 --> 35:17.280
If you see them again,

35:17.350 --> 35:18.280
contact us immediately.

35:19.150 --> 35:19.790
Okay.

35:19.810 --> 35:20.430
Thank you, sir.

35:20.430 --> 35:21.340
The oranges are so sweet.

35:21.350 --> 35:22.240
We'll come again.

35:22.590 --> 35:23.040
Okay!

35:23.070 --> 35:24.030
Okay, thank you.

35:24.050 --> 35:24.430
Bye.

35:24.460 --> 35:25.350
Okay.

35:25.510 --> 35:26.480
Let's go to the industrial park.

35:26.480 --> 35:27.030
Getting stuff?

35:27.150 --> 35:28.110
Coming, coming.

36:07.740 --> 36:08.600
Yue.

36:12.740 --> 36:14.350
This should be the abandoned factory

36:14.350 --> 36:15.180
he mentioned.

36:15.470 --> 36:16.950
Nobody passes by and no surveillance cameras.

36:16.980 --> 36:18.390
It's suitable for criminals to hide.

36:32.110 --> 36:32.750
Yue.

36:37.150 --> 36:38.310
These tire marks are new.

36:44.150 --> 36:45.070
Notify Captain Jiang.

36:51.020 --> 36:51.780
Is it good?

36:52.400 --> 36:53.000
Yes.

36:53.610 --> 36:54.250
It's really good.

36:54.390 --> 36:54.980
How'd you make it?

36:55.200 --> 36:57.250
I followed a recipe.

36:57.910 --> 36:58.650
Try it.

36:59.470 --> 37:00.730
Eat it. It's all for you.

37:03.610 --> 37:04.070
Hello?

37:04.140 --> 37:04.620
Captain Jiang.

37:04.750 --> 37:05.500
We've got a clue.

37:06.030 --> 37:06.770
Text me the address.

37:07.490 --> 37:08.120
I'll be right there.

37:10.790 --> 37:11.360
Sorry.

37:11.390 --> 37:12.010
We have

37:12.230 --> 37:13.080
a mission.

37:13.190 --> 37:14.080
I can't eat with you.

37:16.000 --> 37:17.350
B-Be careful.

37:19.720 --> 37:20.270
Bye.

37:20.870 --> 37:21.580
Be careful.

37:24.180 --> 37:26.910
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

37:39.070 --> 37:40.800
Qiao Rui is in a relationship

37:40.830 --> 37:41.740
with Huang Wei.

37:42.510 --> 37:43.760
Really?

37:45.270 --> 37:46.140
Yan.

37:46.570 --> 37:47.660
An ER patient came.

37:47.690 --> 37:49.210
They said it's the officer Liu Hao

37:49.340 --> 37:50.350
who's always

37:50.350 --> 37:51.030
with Captain Jiang.

37:53.470 --> 37:54.460
Liu Hao?

37:55.680 --> 37:56.760
What’s wrong with him?

37:57.170 --> 37:59.080
I heard he got stabbed

37:59.110 --> 38:00.020
during a mission.

38:00.440 --> 38:01.400
But don't worry.

38:01.420 --> 38:02.800
He's fine now.

38:02.820 --> 38:03.570
Which room?

38:03.820 --> 38:04.520
Room 305.

38:12.000 --> 38:12.720
Dr. Lu.

38:14.900 --> 38:16.760
Please tell your higher-up to let me

38:17.130 --> 38:18.370
be discharged.

38:18.670 --> 38:19.510
I'm really fine.

38:19.580 --> 38:20.270
What?

38:20.310 --> 38:21.430
Just lie down.

38:21.540 --> 38:23.280
I just asked a surgeon.

38:23.360 --> 38:25.230
The stab was just one cm away from your spleen.

38:25.350 --> 38:26.490
It's too dangerous.

38:26.830 --> 38:27.880
Injuries are inevitable

38:27.910 --> 38:29.150
during missions.

38:30.080 --> 38:31.710
I just regret not catching them.

38:31.800 --> 38:33.220
Don't think about that now,

38:33.270 --> 38:33.870
okay?

38:33.910 --> 38:35.310
You must rest well.

38:35.330 --> 38:36.560
Prioritize your health.

38:37.720 --> 38:39.160
Okay, thank you.

38:42.790 --> 38:43.670
Did you

38:43.870 --> 38:46.410
go on the mission with Captain Jiang?

38:46.540 --> 38:47.260
Yes.

38:47.770 --> 38:49.400
I was with Captain Jiang.

39:00.540 --> 39:01.380
Qin Yue.

39:01.590 --> 39:02.160
Jiang.

39:02.320 --> 39:03.150
What happened?

39:03.340 --> 39:04.440
We came here

39:04.470 --> 39:05.400
according to the interviewees.

39:05.470 --> 39:05.950
This park was

39:05.950 --> 39:06.990
abandoned for a long time.

39:07.110 --> 39:08.080
No one usually comes.

39:08.110 --> 39:08.920
But when we got here,

39:08.950 --> 39:10.230
we found new tire marks at the door.

39:10.910 --> 39:11.840
I'm guessing this is

39:11.870 --> 39:13.120
where criminals hide.

39:13.320 --> 39:13.930
Captain Jiang.

39:13.980 --> 39:15.360
This is the map of the factory.

39:15.470 --> 39:16.680
There are four doors in the four directions

39:16.710 --> 39:17.590
and many small doors.

39:17.680 --> 39:18.690
The structure inside is very complex.

39:21.790 --> 39:22.570
Well,

39:22.750 --> 39:23.910
we'll each lead a team

39:23.930 --> 39:24.640
and split up.

39:25.060 --> 39:25.640
Understood.

39:25.670 --> 39:26.030
Jiang.

39:26.070 --> 39:26.880
Don't think I'm superstitious,

39:26.910 --> 39:28.090
but my right eye kept twitching since I woke up.

39:28.120 --> 39:28.940
Be careful.

39:29.220 --> 39:30.200
Everyone, be careful.

39:30.430 --> 39:30.800
Let's go.

39:30.840 --> 39:31.710
Don't jinx it!

39:32.690 --> 39:33.510
Be careful!

39:33.540 --> 39:34.000
Let's go.

39:34.030 --> 39:34.580
Go!

39:34.790 --> 39:35.300
Let's go.

40:04.480 --> 40:05.540
Where is it?

40:06.230 --> 40:07.660
As long as you let me go,

40:07.990 --> 40:09.810
I will give it to you.

40:10.530 --> 40:11.670
Where is it?

40:12.860 --> 40:14.260
Tell him again.

40:15.130 --> 40:16.060
If he lets me go,

40:16.270 --> 40:17.010
I'll leave the country

40:17.030 --> 40:18.330
and never come back.

40:18.350 --> 40:19.550
I promise I'll give it to you.

40:19.590 --> 40:20.890
I didn't back it up.

40:21.340 --> 40:22.240
I'll never come back.

40:22.270 --> 40:23.160
Call him

40:23.190 --> 40:24.840
and talk to him again.

40:25.050 --> 40:26.150
Isn't this good for

40:26.150 --> 40:26.920
both of us?

41:03.670 --> 41:04.190
This way.

41:33.190 --> 41:33.670
Hello?

41:35.070 --> 41:35.760
Not yet.

41:39.510 --> 41:40.340
Got it.

41:44.550 --> 41:45.570
Help!

41:45.600 --> 41:46.890
Is anyone there?

43:53.360 --> 43:54.040
Hao!

43:54.790 --> 43:55.520
Hao!

43:56.440 --> 43:57.080
Hurry.

43:57.470 --> 43:57.950
Go.

43:57.960 --> 43:58.310
Yes.

43:58.350 --> 43:58.710
Go.

43:59.370 --> 44:00.070
Hao.

44:02.980 --> 44:03.640
Press onto it.

44:03.990 --> 44:04.800
Press onto it.

44:05.190 --> 44:06.490
Call an ambulance to the factory.

44:06.620 --> 44:07.690
Someone's injured.

44:09.680 --> 44:10.230
Liu Hao!

44:10.280 --> 44:10.840
Captain Jiang.

44:11.600 --> 44:12.260
What happened?

44:12.280 --> 44:13.160
Captain Jiang.

44:13.260 --> 44:14.070
I was careless.

44:14.090 --> 44:14.950
They ran away.

44:16.440 --> 44:17.270
Did you call an ambulance?

44:17.310 --> 44:17.710
Yes.

44:18.750 --> 44:19.560
How are you?

44:19.590 --> 44:20.360
I’m fine.

44:21.230 --> 44:21.910
Captain Jiang.

44:21.940 --> 44:22.770
I’m here.

44:23.340 --> 44:24.300
There's a situation here.

44:24.600 --> 44:25.400
I'll be right there.

44:25.750 --> 44:26.310
Watch him.

44:26.330 --> 44:26.750
Okay.

44:28.190 --> 44:28.810
Hang in there.

44:28.830 --> 44:29.980
The ambulance will be here soon.

44:31.770 --> 44:33.330
Did he get hurt?

44:34.750 --> 44:36.030
After I got hurt,

44:36.110 --> 44:37.310
I was sent to the hospital.

44:37.880 --> 44:39.700
I don't know what happened later.

44:41.200 --> 44:41.970
Okay.

44:42.550 --> 44:44.030
Anyway, have a good rest.

44:44.900 --> 44:45.430
Okay.

44:45.570 --> 44:46.200
Thank you.

44:48.820 --> 44:49.730
I'll get going.

45:03.870 --> 45:05.820
The murderer deliberately let water out before they ran.

45:06.380 --> 45:07.400
The traces were washed away.

45:30.490 --> 45:31.420
Did you catch them?

45:42.740 --> 45:43.760
Get Forensics here.

45:45.510 --> 45:47.480
Inform the trace inspection officers to get here.

45:47.500 --> 45:48.420
Protect the scene.
